




d		Delete									R	Enter Replace mode
y		Yank (copy)								u	Undo changes
c		Change (delete then insert)				a	Append
x		Delete character						A	Append from end of line
dd		Delete line (Cut)						i	Insert
yy		Yank line (Copy)						o	Next line
p		Paste									O	Previous line
P		Paste before							fc	Go forward to character c
s		Delete char and insert					Fc	Go backward to character c
S		Delete line and insert					gg	First line
C		Delete until end of 					G	Last line
			line and insert	
dd		(repeat the letter) 					>	Indent right
			Delete current line
dw		Delete to next word						<	Indent left
db		Delete to beginning						"="	Autoindent
			 of word
2dd		Delete 2 lines							g~	Swap case
dip		Delete a text object					gU	Uppercase
		 (inside paragraph)		
d		Delete selection						gu	Lowercase
	